ifp.description: his question will be resolved using the Multisensor Analyzed Sea Ice Extent - Northern Hemisphere (MASIE-NH) data reported by NOAA's National Snow & Ice Data Center (http://nsidc.org/data/masie). The relevant data can be accessed by clicking the ‘Download Data’ button, then selecting 'Daily Sea Ice Extent Values: Comma Separated Values (CSV) file' and looking at the column for the relevant region. If the maximum occurs before the close date, the question will be closed retroactively with the first date of the maximum as the end date of the question.
